# 🤖 7. Intégration IA (Ollama)

## Installation

```bash
ollama run llama3
```

## Appel API depuis backend

```js
const axios = require("axios");

const askAI = async (prompt) => {
  const res = await axios.post("http://localhost:11434/api/generate", {
    model: "llama3",
    prompt: prompt,
  });

  return res.data.response;
};
```

---

## 📊 Exemple Audit IA

